methods.name: Run
methods.logic: This method likely executes the Maglev graph building phase of the Turboshaft compiler pipeline. It takes PipelineData, a temporary Zone for memory allocation, and Linkage information as input.  It returns an optional BailoutReason, indicating if the compilation process needs to bail out for some reason. If compilation succeeds, it likely returns std::nullopt.
